  "description": "Application for Listed Building Consent in relation to external and internal works of repair and decoration. External works to include: replacement of the existing UPVC window with a timber window, replacing broken or missing roof slates, securing slipped ones, and carrying out brick repairs and repointing on chimneys. Redressing of lead flashings where needed, and steam cleaning and re-bedding of coping stones.  Replacement of defective sections of guttering. Roof repairs and replacements on the portico entrance and garage. Renewal of damaged sections of fascias and soffits as necessary. Brick repairs and repointing of external walls, with concrete and plaster repairs where required. Restoration of timber sash windows and casement doors, along with concrete windowsills and metal handrails. Internal works (communal areas) to include installation of new LED light fittings and undertaking localised repairs to staircases.",
